      "CVE": "CVE-2021-33640",
      "Description": "After tar_close(), libtar.c releases the memory pointed to by pointer t. After tar_close() is called in the list() function, it continues to use pointer t: free_longlink_longname(t-\u003eth_buf) . As a result, the released memory is used (use-after-free).",
